Output demo/demo.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 600
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "export PATH=$HOME/.cargo/bin:/opt/homebrew/bin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin && export PS1='$ ' && clear" Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "cargo run --release" Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 2s

